bottom:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:18px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">280,000~315,000엔(JPY)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:22px;\">\n<td style=\"width:155px;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:22px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">4주 프로그램</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:230px;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:22px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">2026. 6. 14.(일) ~ 7. 12.(일)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:217px;border:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:22px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">360,000~410,000엔(JPY)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">3. 선발인원 : 약간명</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">4. 프로그램 세부내용 : </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.mwt-mice.com/events/komstudy2026/\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">https://www.mwt-mice.com/events/komstudy2026/</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">5. 지원자격</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">가. 2026-1학기 본교 1학기~7</span>학기(편입생은 1학기~3학기) 재학생</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:22.4pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">※ 정규 8학기(편입생은4</span>학기) 이상 재학생, 휴학생, 수료생, 대학원생은 불가</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:22.4pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">※ 2026.8월 졸업 또는 수료 예정인 재학생 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">나. 일본어 입문 및 초급자 (JLPT N5~N4수준, JLPT </span>등 공인어학증명서 제출 불요)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">다. 고마자와대학 명시한 프로그램 참가 및 신청자격을 충족시키는 자</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">6. 신청기한 : 2026. 4. 5.(일)까지</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">7. 신청방법</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">가. 고마자와대학 Online Application 및 nDRIMS </span>신청</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:22.4pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">※ nDRIMS 신청 : 학사행정 - [학생신청]</span>신청함 - [국제교류] <span style=\"color:black;\">국제교류신청 –</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\"> '2026/여름학기' 및</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:22.4pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">     언어권 '일본어' </span>선택)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">    나. 고마자와대학 Online Application 및 본교 nDRIMS </span>신청을 모두 마쳐야 정상적으로</span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">신청 완료</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">    다. 고마자와대학 프로그램 전체 모집정원을 충족할 경우 신청접수가 조기 마감될 수 </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">있으니,</span>  </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">         참가를 희망하는 경우에는 빠르게 신청할 것을 권장함(별도의 동국대  배정</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">정원 없음)</span></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height:17.0pt;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other;word-break:keep-all;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">8. 프로그램 참가자 선발계획 </span></span></span></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:25px;\">\n<td style=\"width:73px;border:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;background:#FFF7CC;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:25px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">구<span style=\"color:black;\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">분</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:66px;border:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;background:#FFF7CC;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:25px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">평가주체</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:493px;border-top:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:none;background:#FFF7CC;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:25px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">평가 및 선발방법</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:70px;\">\n<td style=\"width:73px;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:70px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">1차</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:66px;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:70px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">고마</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">자와대</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:493px;border:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:70px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">ㆍ[신청자] 고마자와대 Online Application </span>→[고마자와대] 평가 및 참가여부 확정</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">ㆍ고마자와대 프로그램 모집정원(40명) 도달 시 신청접수가 조기 마감될 수</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\">  <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">있으니, 참가를 희망하는 경우에는 빠르게 신청할 것을 권장함</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:65px;\">\n<td style=\"width:73px;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:65px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">2차</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">(장학생</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">선발평가)</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:66px;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;border-right:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:65px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">동국대</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:493px;border:none;border-bottom:solid black 1.0pt;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:65px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">ㆍ고마자와대로부터 참가승인을 받은 재학생을 대상으로 글로벌교류팀에서 평가</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\">  <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">※ 평가항목 : 학점, 수학계획서 등</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">ㆍ평가에 관한 세부내용은 해당자 대상으로 별도 안내</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">9. 장학금 지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">가. 프로그램 참가자로 선발된 학생 중, 아래 ‘장학금 수혜조건’ 을 충족시키는 참가자</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">에게는  해외 </span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">    단기연수 장학금 지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">   </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">※ 장학금 지급예정액 : 1,000,000원/인, </span>재원: 대학혁신지원사업</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">   나. 장학금은 프로그램을 정상적으로 이수한 학생에게 연수 종료 후 지급하며, 프로그램 </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">미수료  및 </span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">        중도포기 귀국자 등에는 미지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">   다. 장학금액은 변경될 수 있으며, 장학금액 및 장학금 수혜를 위한 제출서류 및</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"> <span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">유의사항은 합격자 </span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">        대상으로 별도 안내 예정</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">   라. 장학금 수혜 조건</span></span></span></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:153px;\">\n<td style=\"width:613px;border:solid black 1.0pt;background:#FCF5E7;padding:1.5pt 5.25pt 1.5pt 5.25pt;height:153px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">‣<span style=\"color:black;\"> 2026-1학기 본교 1학기~7학기(</span>편입생은 1</span>학기~3학기) 재학생</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">※ 정규 8학기(편입생은 4</span>학기) </span>이상 재학생, 휴학생, 수료생, 대학원생은 불가</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">※ 2026.8월에 졸업 또는 수료 예정인 재학생 불가</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">‣ 2025학년도 동</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">‧하계 해외 단기연수 장학금 수혜자 불가</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">‣ 2026학년도 타 해외연수 장학(학생처 주관 해외탐방, 해외봉사 등 대혁신지원사업</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">국고재원장학) 수혜자 및 수혜예정자(참가예정자) </span>중복수급 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\"><span style=\"color:black;\">‣ 기타 해외 여행에 결격사유가 없는 자</span></span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">10. 기 타</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">가. 2026 하계 해외 단기 연수 프로그램 중복지원 불가</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">   (일본 및 타 언어권 프로그램 합격(합격을 포기한 경우에도) 후 중복지원 불가)</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">나. 프로그램에 참가하여 이수하더라도, 학적상태 변동(</span>졸업, 수료 등), 타 해외연수</span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">참가에 따른</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">     장학금 수혜 등, 해외 단기연수 장학금 수혜조건을 충족시키지 못하는</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">  사안이 확인되는 경우</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">     에는 장학금 미지급</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:11.2pt;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:.1pt;\">11. 문의 : 신공학관 9층 글로벌교류팀(02-2260-3463)</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial;\"><strong><span style=\"color:black;\">                                     국제처 글로벌교류팀</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"display: none;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:17.0pt;\"> </p>",
